Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易打敗木偶獸的孩子們 再度踏入另一個新的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而小光卻因為發燒臥病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一等人外出四處尋找感冒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻遇到了黑暗四天王之中的 第三位殺手機械邪龍獸狂風暴雨似的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他們躲過一劫 以為可以再見到小光的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限大炮爆炸的威力把太一等人震落到了深淵之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四十九話「再見 鼻涕獸」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒過來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿岳 迪路獸 我怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在感覺如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒好像已經退了 現在覺得身體舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你剛才昏睡了很久 不過好像對你的身體反而有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人去哪裏了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他們找到誰了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小光 太好了 你終於醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一他們呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒有在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許太一和光子郎他們掉到別的地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這個 這個是比丘獸找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你生病了 太一他們好不容易才找到感冒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近的路就像是一個迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我們一起出去找 一定可以找到到他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀 打起精神來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也一定會努力去找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是他的妹妹呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是現實世界的地底下?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空也這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為上面是現實世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜一點 你們有沒有聽到什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吧? 不知道是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音好像是從那邊傳過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點轉! 認真工作! 不許有人偷懶!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些見不得陽光又沒有用的鼻涕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就是機械邪龍獸大王所控制的 黑暗龍卷山上巨大城市的動力和能源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點工作吧! 一直工作到死為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是熊仔獸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不是熊仔獸 是惡霸熊仔獸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡霸熊仔獸?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡霸熊仔獸 雖然和熊仔獸長得有點相像 但它長相非常兇惡可怕的玩具型數碼寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的個性就如名字一樣 絕招是「心碎一擊」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也是機械邪龍獸的部下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來它也是機械帝國軍團的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼? 還不快點給我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕獸好可憐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼? 快工作!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作 工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 看你們往哪裏逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪路獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪路獸 我沒事 你不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點讓鼻涕獸們恢復自由 拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追得到我們你就來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些小鬼 別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比丘獸進化…巴多拉獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴達獸進化…天使獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是能量不足嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空 怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只好溜之大吉了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空 你看我在飛 我從來沒有飛得這麼快過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿岳 我也是 我飛得好快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個逃命逃到脫離現實了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光…小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕獸們在呼喊著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光…小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕獸 你們在這裏幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼? 這種眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 是誰把鼻涕獸身上的鏈子給打開的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開鎖的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去保護小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你、你們想幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去保護小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是輸給鼻涕獸我就不叫做惡霸熊仔獸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這、這是什麼光芒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身體裏面充滿能量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得能量多到快要溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪路獸超進化…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比丘獸進化…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴多拉獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴達獸進化…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想、想打架是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就連你們一起收拾掉 看我的厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隕石巨翼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天堂之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕獸 你還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕 鼻涕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個樣子 你應該很快就會好起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是代表小光的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光芒會帶領我們前進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們只要跟著光往前走就可以找到太一他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 就把我們要走的路交給你的光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械邪龍獸大王 機械邪龍獸大王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是惡霸熊仔獸嗎? 什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個被選召的孩子和他們的數碼寶貝來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在你的管轄區域裏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要討機械邪龍獸大王的歡心 我很勇敢地和他們戰鬥 可是還是被打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你發現那幾個小鬼的行蹤 竟然沒有通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才跟那幾個小鬼的數碼寶貝戰鬥的時候受了點傷 傷口好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械邪龍獸大王 求求你救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那幾個小鬼在哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再留著你也沒有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞古獸 你在幹什麼? 快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 亞古獸和甲蟲獸都已經很累了 我們先休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的 我也累得快撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 你冷靜一下好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你也一定累得快受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光…她在發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我們都知道小光生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道 那你就不要指使我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太、太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指使你? 我什麼時候指使你了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再煩我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你簡直不明事理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都冷靜一點好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有誰跟在我們後面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們躲在門口面 然後假裝還在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然真的動手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打你又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎 不要打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是機械邪龍獸的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲蟲獸進化…比多獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞古獸進化…暴龍獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴龍獸…暴龍獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞古獸 你們應該是太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我知道你真的很擔心小光的病才會這麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要負起責任 我去戰鬥好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們同心協力 一定有辦法打敗它們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路獸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路獸 曾經在文件島見過的改造人型數碼寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次因為比多獸幫忙 取出身上的黑色齒輪才得以解放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒有想到居然會是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才沒想到是你呢 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 安杜路獸 你在這個地方做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我躲在機械邪龍獸所控制的城市底下從事反抗活動 我希望能夠解救那些被暴力所控制的數碼寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我還以為你們幾個是機械邪龍獸的部下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就打起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在找一個名字叫做小光的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我猜測 阿空和阿岳也跟她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣 請你們稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你幫幫忙 小光是太一的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光要來這個地方了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裏呀 被選召的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械邪龍獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路獸也在這裏 正好可以把你們一次解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快點先找一個地方躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說太一他們?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械邪龍獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空 阿岳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光\N光子郎 甲蟲獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械邪龍獸跟你們發生衝突了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路獸為了保護我們正在跟它戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它說它在地底下從事反抗活動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隕石巨翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天堂之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋轉能量劍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械邪龍獸是究極體數碼寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些不堪一擊的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就輪到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 儘是一些老弱殘兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也想跟我戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕獸!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體…充滿了能量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞古獸究極進化…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥暴龍獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 振作一點 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我還有太一和小光 大家都跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不——!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市的控制者機械邪龍獸被打敗了 這個地區也要開始崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心 有我們在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏恐怕也岌岌可危了 大家趕快離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市消失了 我的任務也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 等我們到地面去 為鼻涕獸它們做個墳墓好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一起來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等著吧 小丑皇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一等人好不容易到了黑暗龍卷山的山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻遇上另外一隻可怕的數碼寶貝妖女獸的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女獸上前抵擋 與她戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一場光明與黑暗之女的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回數碼寶貝大冒險\N「女性對決 妖女獸!」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 冒險越來越深入了

